name: Team 1
body:
### Welcome to Team_1 Page.
We've created this webpage using the automatic page generator from github. We thought that could be a good idea to show to all the public the amazing stuff that we were developing during the following sessions in module 4.

### Paper
We’ve documented all the coding stuff in a [paper](https://www.sharelatex.com/project/56a4a0c0fd40a0120dcecab6/output/output.pdf?cache_bust=1454084323437&compileGroup=standard&build=1528e2df777). In this paper the following points will be described:

* Motivation
* Related work
* Your system
* Evaluation
* Conclusions
* References


### Presentation
We’ve created a [presentation](https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/). We decided to link it to slideshare to have it available for the people who is interested in.

### Authors and Contributors
This are the people who did that practices:
* Sergi Canyameres Masip (@scanyameres)
* Dèlia Fernández Cañellas (@deliafc)
* Jordi Frias Navarro (@Txordi00)
* Arcadi Llanza Carmona (@alc1218)

### Support or Contact
